{"tid":2326960,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【背後真面目】女大學生為慳開支與5名OL合租 深夜偷看客廳驚揭室友隱藏恐怖陰謀","createTime":"2020-12-15T16:41:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-15T18:25:00.000Z","uid":224375,"like":0,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"09000f43668bf8f6390756f1e214dd48cb444b9b","tid":2326960,"uid":224375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T16:41:58.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\">屌你個老味，痴撚線</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n日本一名女大學生為慳開支住合租屋，5名OL室友看似和善，該名女大學生與5人相處融洽，并放下戒心，豈料有一天，她深夜聽見客廳隱約傳來詭異的聲音和光線，好奇心下前往偷看，驚揭5名室友實藏恐怖陰謀。<br />\n<br />\n日本節目《爆報！THEフライデー》近期收到一位女觀眾加藤投稿，分享她早前住合租屋的恐怖經歷，期望其他人聽到她的故事後能汲取教訓。加藤稱，自己今年18歲，是剛考上東京的大學一年級，為了節省開支，她決定租住租金便宜的Share House。<br />\n<br />\n這間合租屋非常便宜，一個月只需5萬日圓，共有5名OL室友，她們給人感覺是非常隨和、友善且斯文，加藤很快就與她們打成一片，亦放下了戒心。但隨著相處時間愈長，加藤愈感到不對勁&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2829259/%E3%80%90%E8%83%8C%E5%BE%8C%E7%9C%9F%E9%9D%A2%E7%9B%AE%E3%80%91%E5%A5%B3%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E7%82%BA%E6%85%B3%E9%96%8B%E6%94%AF%E8%88%875%E5%90%8DOL%E5%90%88%E7%A7%9F%20%20%E6%B7%B1%E5%A4%9C%E5%81%B7%E7%9C%8B%E5%AE%A2%E5%BB%B3%E9%A9%9A%E6%8F%AD%E5%AE%A4%E5%8F%8B%E9%9A%B1%E8%97%8F%E6%81%90%E6%80%96%E9%99%B0%E8%AC%80?r=mcsdfb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2829259%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E8%2583%258C%25E5%25BE%258C%25E7%259C%259F%25E9%259D%25A2%25E7%259B%25AE%25E3%2580%2591%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F%25E7%2582%25BA%25E6%2585%25B3%25E9%2596%258B%25E6%2594%25AF%25E8%2588%25875%25E5%2590%258DOL%25E5%2590%2588%25E7%25A7%259F%2520%2520%25E6%25B7%25B1%25E5%25A4%259C%25E5%2581%25B7%25E7%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E5%25BB%25B3%25E9%25A9%259A%25E6%258F%25AD%25E5%25AE%25A4%25E5%258F%258B%25E9%259A%25B1%25E8%2597%258F%25E6%2581%2590%25E6%2580%2596%25E9%2599%25B0%25E8%25AC%2580%3Fr%3Dmcsdfb&d=ZAqn3h4t0e4XfOyVRCtvGH4HMPoqNxaa4E9h32y1mRE%3D&h=86a2e319\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2829259/%E3%80%90%E8%83%8C%E5%BE%8C%E7%9C%9F%E9%9D%A2%E7%9B%AE%E3%80%91%E5%A5%B3%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E7%82%BA%E6%85%B3%E9%96%8B%E6%94%AF%E8%88%875%E5%90%8DOL%E5%90%88%E7%A7%9F%20%20%E6%B7%B1%E5%A4%9C%E5%81%B7%E7%9C%8B%E5%AE%A2%E5%BB%B3%E9%A9%9A%E6%8F%AD%E5%AE%A4%E5%8F%8B%E9%9A%B1%E8%97%8F%E6%81%90%E6%80%96%E9%99%B0%E8%AC%80?r=mcsdfb</a>"},{"pid":"42d2b30d7ffc1e795dbe840cc2f1fefdc8b81e39","tid":2326960,"uid":236368,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T16:46:22.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"large\">on99，馮紹波就咪撚貼link啦</span></span>"},{"pid":"b7eb30ac7028262850d48db99db1bb44cc8203a5","tid":2326960,"uid":149266,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T16:50:02.000Z","msg":"總結: 四個邪教女仔想焗個租客入教<br />\n完<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c576560e902bb0a20329d1ffd7cd2798a7092e36","tid":2326960,"uid":224375,"like":0,"dislike":14,"score":-14,"quote":{"pid":"42d2b30d7ffc1e795dbe840cc2f1fefdc8b81e39","tid":2326960,"uid":236368,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T16:46:22.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"large\">on99，馮紹波就咪撚貼link啦</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T16:52:03.000Z","msg":"我貼乜關你撚事咩社會垃圾  <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkg